# Push workflow (SMB Health Supply)

When the user says **push**, they mean both:

1. **GitHub** — stage, commit, and `git push origin main`
2. **Vercel** — `vercel deploy --prod` from `site/`

Do not push to only one unless the user explicitly asks for GitHub-only or Vercel-only.

- Repository: https://github.com/lowdifficulty/smb-health-supply
- Deploy directory: `site/`
- Production URL: https://smbhealthsupply.com

After GitHub is connected in Vercel (Settings → Git), pushes to `main` may auto-deploy; still run `vercel deploy --prod` from `site/` if auto-deploy is not enabled.
